openapi: 3.0.0 info: description: TickHistory provides dynamic access to historical tick data for a specific security for specific dates or date range. title: TickHistory version: 1.0.0 servers: - url: https://api-sandbox.factset.com/bulk-documents/tickhistory security: - FactSetApiKey: [] - FactSetOAuth2: [] paths: /v1/request-files: get: description: Try it Out - references a Sandbox environment to simulate live reponses.

**In Sandbox** data available from 20210101 to 20210131. Current date data is not available.

PROD has data from 20120101 to current date &

**available IDs is limited to..**

US Equity - IBM-USA, F-USA, AAPL-USA, GOOG-USA

ASX - CBA-ASX, BHP-ASX

LSE - HSBA-LON, VOD-LON

Tokyo - 7203-TKS, 4307-TKS

Swiss - NESN-SWX, COTN-SWX

Singapore - J36-SES &

Hong Kong - 700-HKG

parameters: - description: any ticker.

**Either ticker(s) + iso_code (OR) product is allowed**

**NOTE**:Only one identifier can be requested per request examples: fieldname1: summary: US Equity value: IBM,F,AAPL,GOOG fieldname2: summary: ASX value: CBA,BHP fieldname3: summary: LSE value: HSBA,VOD fieldname4: summary: Tokyo value: 7203,4307 fieldname5: summary: Swiss value: NESN,COTN fieldname6: summary: Singapore value: J36 fieldname7: summary: HongKong value: 700 explode: true in: query name: ticker required: false schema: type: string style: form - description: iso_code.

ticker(s) + iso_code

**Does not support multiple iso_codes**

examples: fieldname1: summary: US Equity value: USA fieldname2: summary: ASX value: AUS fieldname3: summary: LSE value: LON fieldname4: summary: Tokyo value: TKS fieldname5: summary: Swiss value: SWX fieldname6: summary: Singapore value: SES fieldname7: summary: HongKong value: HKG explode: true in: query name: iso_code required: false schema: type: string style: form - description: Fields for which data is requested.
